---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';

const slug        = 'privacy-policy';
const title       = 'Privacy Policy — FreemarketingCalculator.com';
const description = 'Privacy policy for FreemarketingCalculator.com. Learn how we handle data, cookies, and advertising on our free marketing calculator tools.';
const updated     = 'July 6, 2026';

const schema = {
  "@type": "WebPage",
  "name": "Privacy Policy",
  "url": "https://freemarketingcalculator.com/privacy-policy/",
  "publisher": { "@id": "https://freemarketingcalculator.com/#org" }
};
---

<Base title={title} description={description} slug={slug} schema={[schema]}>
  <section class="page-hero" aria-labelledby="pp-h1">
    <div class="container">
      <p class="eyebrow">Legal</p>
      <h1 id="pp-h1">Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p class="citation">Last updated: {updated}</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <div class="container">
    <div class="content-section prose" style="max-width: 680px; margin: 0 auto;">

      <h2>1. Overview</h2>
      <p>
        FreemarketingCalculator.com ("we", "us", "our") operates the website at
        https://freemarketingcalculator.com. This Privacy Policy explains what information
        we collect, how we use it, and your rights regarding that information.
      </p>
      <p>
        We take privacy seriously. We do not sell your personal data. We do not require
        account registration or email submission to use any calculator on this site.
      </p>

      <h2>2. Information We Collect</h2>
      <p><strong>Information you provide:</strong> None. Our calculators run entirely
      in your browser. The numbers you enter are never sent to our servers and are
      not stored anywhere.</p>

      <p><strong>Information collected automatically:</strong> When you visit this site,
      standard web server logs and analytics tools may collect:</p>
      <ul style="margin: var(--space-3) 0; padding-left: var(--space-6); color: var(--text-mid); line-height: 1.9;">
        <li>Your IP address (anonymised)</li>
        <li>Browser type and version</li>
        <li>Pages visited and time spent</li>
        <li>Referring website or search query</li>
        <li>Device type (desktop/mobile)</li>
      </ul>
      <p>This data is collected in aggregate and is not linked to any identifiable individual.</p>

      <h2>3. Cookies</h2>
      <p>This site uses cookies from the following third-party services:</p>

      <p><strong>Google Analytics (GA4):</strong> We use Google Analytics to understand
      how visitors use the site — which pages are popular, where traffic comes from, and
      how long people stay. Google Analytics uses cookies to track sessions. You can
      opt out at <a href="https://tools.google.com/dlpage/gaoptout" target="_blank" rel="noopener">tools.google.com/dlpage/gaoptout</a>.</p>

      <p><strong>Google AdSense:</strong> We display advertisements served by Google
      AdSense. Google uses cookies to show you relevant ads based on your interests and
      browsing history. You can manage ad personalisation at
      <a href="https://adssettings.google.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener">adssettings.google.com</a>
      or opt out of personalised advertising at
      <a href="https://www.aboutads.info/choices/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">aboutads.info/choices</a>.</p>

      <p><strong>Cloudflare:</strong> This site is served via Cloudflare's CDN network.
      Cloudflare may set performance and security cookies. See
      <a href="https://www.cloudflare.com/privacypolicy/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Cloudflare's Privacy Policy</a>.</p>

      <h2>4. How We Use Information</h2>
      <p>Automatically collected data is used solely to:</p>
      <ul style="margin: var(--space-3) 0; padding-left: var(--space-6); color: var(--text-mid); line-height: 1.9;">
        <li>Understand which calculators are most useful</li>
        <li>Improve site performance and content</li>
        <li>Detect and prevent abuse or malicious traffic</li>
      </ul>
      <p>We do not use your data for marketing, profiling, or sale to third parties.</p>

      <h2>5. Google Advertising</h2>
      <p>
        We participate in the Google AdSense programme. Google, as a third-party vendor,
        uses cookies (including the DoubleClick cookie) to serve ads on this site based
        on a user's prior visits to this and other websites. Users may opt out of
        personalised advertising by visiting
        <a href="https://www.google.com/settings/ads" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Google Ads Settings</a>.
      </p>
      <p>
        We comply with Google's publisher policies. We do not place ads adjacent to
        calculator buttons or in ways that could cause accidental clicks.
      </p>

      <h2>6. Data Retention</h2>
      <p>
        Analytics data is retained for 14 months in Google Analytics, after which it is
        automatically deleted. Server logs are retained for up to 30 days by our hosting
        provider (Cloudflare) for security purposes.
      </p>

      <h2>7. Your Rights</h2>
      <p>Depending on your location, you may have rights to:</p>
      <ul style="margin: var(--space-3) 0; padding-left: var(--space-6); color: var(--text-mid); line-height: 1.9;">
        <li>Access data we hold about you</li>
        <li>Request correction or deletion of your data</li>
        <li>Opt out of analytics and advertising cookies</li>
        <li>Lodge a complaint with your local data protection authority</li>
      </ul>
      <p>
        Since we collect no personal data beyond standard server logs, most requests
        can be satisfied by opting out of Google Analytics and disabling cookies in
        your browser settings.
      </p>

      <h2>8. Children's Privacy</h2>
      <p>
        This site is not directed at children under 13. We do not knowingly collect
        any data from children. If you believe a child has submitted personal information,
        contact us at hello@freemarketingcalculator.com and we will delete it immediately.
      </p>

      <h2>9. Changes to This Policy</h2>
      <p>
        We may update this policy as the site evolves. Changes will be reflected in the
        "Last updated" date at the top of this page. Continued use of the site after
        changes constitutes acceptance of the revised policy.
      </p>

      <h2>10. Contact</h2>
      <p>
        For privacy-related questions or requests, contact us at
        <a href="mailto:hello@freemarketingcalculator.com">hello@freemarketingcalculator.com</a>.
      </p>

    </div>
  </div>
</Base>
